      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: July 21, 1949",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, NEW ORLEANS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS AND SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "For the Bureau's information, several citizens in the community of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Alexandria, Louisiana, have recently reportedly seen flying discs. The Alexan-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "dria, Louisiana daily paper has carried numerous articles concerning this.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "At a recent meeting of the Young Mens Business Club in Alexandria,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "a member suggested that since Alexandria, Louisiana is known as a convention city,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the club should try promoting a convention of flying saucer seers. This particu-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "lar comment appeared in the Alexandria paper and was picked up by the AP lines.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] a member of the Young Mens Business Club, advised",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] that since the AP release, they have received a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "large number of requests regarding the convention of flying saucer seers from many",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "parts of the United States. Mr. [REDACTED] states that the interest of the people",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "is evidenced by their inquiries about convention particulars, stating they are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "flying saucer seers and want to attend such a convention.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "This gentleman further advised that in view of the volume of inquiries",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "coming in, it appears that the YMBC will have to hire an employee to handle all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "the correspondence. It might be noted that he advised a representative of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Air Force from Barksdale Field, Louisiana, has inquired as to plans of a flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "saucer convention, stating that they are interested in furnishing an observer if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "such a convention were held.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "This information is being furnished the Bureau, as it is possible such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "an enterprise may cause people to falsify that they have seen flying discs or fly-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "ing saucers. Such falsifications might be made so that they might attend such a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "convention or become official delegates thereto.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
